'''山姆·加拉赫'''（'''{{lang-en|Sam Gallagher}}'''，{{bd|1995年|9月15日}}）是[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]的一位足球運動員，在場上司職前鋒。他現在效力於[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]，他出自普利茅斯的青訓營。他也同時代表過蘇格蘭和英格蘭的青年國家隊參加過比賽<ref>{{cite web|first=Jamie|last=Reid|title=Noel Blake names England U19s squad for Turkey fixture|url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2014/feb/blake-names-u19s-squad-for-turkey|publisher=The Football Association|date=24 February 2014|accessdate=24 February 2014|archive-date=2014-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228230938/http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2014/feb/blake-names-u19s-squad-for-turkey|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Jim|last=Lucas|title=Four Saints in England U19 squad|url=http://www.saintsfc.co.uk/news/article/four-saints-in-young-lions-squad-1379967.aspx|publisher=Southampton FC|date=24 February 2014|accessdate=24 February 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924121711/http://www.saintsfc.co.uk/news/article/four-saints-in-young-lions-squad-1379967.aspx|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>[http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2014/mar/england-v-turkey-match-report "England U19 3–0 Turkey"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2014/mar/england-v-turkey-match-report |date=20140819224512 }} TheFA.com. 5 March 2014. Retrieved 5 March 2014.</ref>。

